AlgorithmMetadata.Name: Bioclim
AlgorithmMetadata.Author: Nix, H. A.
AlgorithmMetadata.Overview: Uses mean and standard deviation for each environmental variable separately to calculate bioclimatic envelops. Level of fitness between the environmental values on a point and the respective envelops classifies points as Suitable, Marginal, or Unsuitable for presence.
